- Reset the drone i.e. unplug the battery and reconnect it

- Make sure your laptop is connected to the wifi of the drone, and that the drone is reachable : 192.168.1.1. The default wifi network is "ardrone2_132997"

- Install the wpa supplicant ability
$ script/install

- Configure the wifi to which the drone will connect
$ script/connect "DroneStaff" -p "donttrytohackthisdronenottakingoff" -a 172.16.5.2

- or simply:
setup-drone.sh

You should be able to telnet the drone on its configured address.


